WHO WE ARE
/$
$
/$
$
We have a passion for coffee, beer and beaches so when we stumbled upon Back Alley, we were in love. Long story short, after years of vacationing to this amazing island, we were determined to make it our home someday. When we found Back Alley was avaliable, it was like the planets aligned just for us and it was destined to be! Needless to say, we had to make this happen. We are very fortunate to be a part of this community and we apprecaite it every day.
​
If we are not at the shop, you might find us at the beach or at a local brewery or coffee shop.. you know.. doing research :)
​
-Travis, Heather, Brianna & Malia
​
